Package org.pikater.shared.database.jpa

This package contains classes, that are implementing access to database using Java Persistence API (JPA).

See: Description

    Class Description
    EntityManagerInstancesCreator
    EntityManagerInstancesCreater is a class, that is used to create EntityManager objects used by Data Access Objects.
    JPAAbstractEntity
    From JPAAbstractEntity class are all JPA entity classes inherited, that are used for database access.
    JPAAgentInfo
    Class JPAAgentInfo represents a record about an agent available in pikater.

Package org.pikater.shared.database.jpa Description

This package contains classes, that are implementing access to database using Java Persistence API (JPA).

This particular package contains JPA entity classes with JPA- prefix in their class names.

Functionality for retrieving and creating these entities are within subpackage org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.daos.

See Also:
org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.daos
